  "explanation": "DP: dp[i][j] is true if s[:i] matches p[:j]. '*' can match empty sequence or any sequence (dp[i-1][j] or dp[i][j-1]).",
  "answer": "def isMatch(s, p):\n    m, n = len(s), len(p); dp = [[False]*(n+1) for _ in range(m+1)]; dp[0][0] = True\n    for j in range(1, n+1): \n        if p[j-1] == '*': dp[0][j] = dp[0][j-1]\n    for i in range(1, m+1):\n        for j in range(1, n+1):\n            if p[j-1] == '*': dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j] or dp[i][j-1]\n            elif p[j-1] in [s[i-1], '?']: dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j-1]\n    return dp[m][n]",
